reviewText: Bought the new Ab Doer...didn't care for the work out that it came with ...so I purchased the original ones on VHS...they are so much better ...I'm actually going to have my VHS  tapes converted to DVD's.

This program provides an excellent workout and utilizes the ab-doer very well. I would recommend this to anyone who has had the ab-doer and not used it often. The program is done every other day which makes it is easier to keep on track with the exercises.
